divs: sighting detailsim driving home from work, it takes me about 2-4 minutes to get home. i'm driving home. i park the car and when i get out i see a bullet\missle\cigar object to the left of me. i was unsure of what it was so i decided to take a picture of it. it was traveling away from me in a diagonal line. i just look up and i see something that does not look like anything i've seen before and i thought about what is was? it then hit me possibly a ufo? it was a rather cloudy night since it rained most of the day.
